			   smew in Haskell

* Installation

- Install GHC (Glasgow Haskell Compiler)
	http://haskell.org/ghc/

- Install the "cabal" command whose package name is cabal-install
	http://hackage.haskell.org/trac/hackage/wiki/CabalInstall

- Install HDBC-sqlite3

  Note that cabal refers to the HTTP_PROXY environment variable.
  % sudo env HTTP_PROXY=$(YOUR_PROXY) cabal $(COMMAND)

	% cabal update
	% cabal list
	% cabal list --installed

	% cabal install HDBC-sqlite3 --dry-run
	% cabal install HDBC-sqlite3

- Compile smew
	% make

  Note that this may displays warnings. Please ignore them.
